Title: Whistle Past the Graveyard
Writer: Graham Yost (developed for television by), Chris Provenzano, Elmore Leonard (short story "Fire in the Hole"), Leonard Chang (story editor)
Actors: Timothy Olyphant, Nick Searcy, Jere Burns, Joelle Carter
Plot: Raylan helps Wendy track down Kendal Crowe after he disappears with an "uncle," while Boyd and the rest of the Crowe family try to get their drugs and dead bodies back across the Mexican border.
